<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437932>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Collected specimens (A–C), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (D–F). A. Rhagovelia elegans, apterous male from Pinheiros, Espírito Santo (−18.3672, −40.1399). B. Rhagovelia hambletoni, apterous male from Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4947, −42.2662). C. Rhagovelia itatiaiana, apterous male from Rio de Janeiro, RJ (−22.9675, −43.4453). D. Rhagovelia elegans. E. Rhagovelia hambletoni. F. Rhagovelia itatiaiana. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437932/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

